full_summary:
# Government Tender Announcement

## Title
Supply of Cabling Tools and Connectors

## Solicitation Number
W6369-230331

## Service Category
General Management (GD)

## Request for Proposal
The Department of National Defence is requesting proposals for the supply of Cabling Tools and Connectors.

## Background
The Department of National Defence has a need for the provision of Cabling Tools and Connectors to support the development of its communication infrastructure.

## Requirements
The following documents are attached to this request for proposals:

* Request for Proposal (RFP) document
* Amendment 001 to the RFP document
* Amendment 002 to the RFP document

The RFP document outlines the requirements for the supply of Cabling Tools and Connectors, including the necessary specifications and delivery requirements.

## Bidder Information
Bidders are required to submit a proposal that meets the requirements outlined in the RFP document. Proposals must be submitted electronically through the Canada Buys website.

## Evaluation Criteria
The proposals will be evaluated based on the following criteria:

* Technical capability to meet the requirements outlined in the RFP document
* Price and terms of delivery

## Contact Information
For any questions or clarification on this request for proposals, please contact:

Rachel Desjardins
Department of National Defence
101 Colonel By Dr, Ottawa, ON K1A 0K2
TEL: 613-290-5359
EMAIL: [rachel.desjardins@forces.gc.ca](mailto:rachel.desjardins@forces.gc.ca)

## Closing Date and Time
Submissions must be received by 2:00 PM EST on October 11, 2022.

Note: I've taken the liberty of rephrasing the content of the original text to make it more concise and easier to read while maintaining the essential information. I've also removed unnecessary details to stay within the 400-word limit. 

Please let me know if there are any changes you would like me to make!
